        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="路由"><a href="#路由" class="headerlink" title="路由"></a>路由</h2><p>根据不同的<strong>url</strong>地址展示不同的内容会页面</p><p>一个针对 <strong>React</strong>而设计的路由解决方案，可以友好的帮你解决 <strong>React components</strong>到 <strong>url</strong> 之间的同步映射关系</p><h3 id="路由用法"><a href="#路由用法" class="headerlink" title="路由用法"></a>路由用法</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">function App() &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">return(</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;HashRouter&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​ &lt;RoutRouteres&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​       // &lt;Route path=&#x27;/&#x27; element=&#123;&lt;Film/&gt;&#125;&gt;&lt;/Route&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​ &lt;Route **index** element=&#123;&lt;Film/&gt;&#125;&gt;&lt;/Route&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​        &lt;Route path=&#x27;/film&#x27; element=&#123;&lt;Film/&gt;&#125;&gt;&lt;/Route&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​        &lt;Route path=&#x27;/cinema&#x27; element=&#123;&lt;Cinema/&gt;&#125;&gt;&lt;/Route&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​        &lt;Route path=&#x27;/center&#x27; element=&#123;&lt;Center/&gt;&#125;&gt;&lt;/Route&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​      &lt;/Routes&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;/HashRouter&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>index</strong>用于嵌套路由，仅仅匹配父路径时，设置渲染的组件</p><p>解决当嵌套路由有多个子路由但本身无法确认默认渲染那个子路由时，可以增加<strong>index</strong>属性来指定默认路由，index路由和其他路由不同的地方就是它没有path属性，它和父路由共享一个路径。</p><h3 id="路由重定向"><a href="#路由重定向" class="headerlink" title="路由重定向"></a>路由重定向</h3><h4 id="Navigate"><a href="#Navigate" class="headerlink" title="Navigate"></a>Navigate</h4><p><code>&lt;Route path=&#39;*&#39; element=&#123;&lt;Navigate to=&quot;/film&quot;/&gt;&#125;&gt;&lt;/Route&gt;</code></p><p>***** 表示任意未定义的路径都会切换到重定义的路径</p><h4 id="自定义Redirect"><a href="#自定义Redirect" class="headerlink" title="自定义Redirect"></a>自定义Redirect</h4><p>外部重新定义一个组件Redirect，导入App</p><p><code>&lt;Route path=&#39;*&#39; element=&#123;&lt;Redierct to=&quot;/film&quot;/&gt;&#125;&gt;&lt;/Route&gt;</code></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">export default function Redirect(&#123;to&#125;) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">const navigate = useNavigate()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">useEffect(()=&gt;&#123; </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​    navigate(to,&#123;replace:true&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;,[])</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">return (null)&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="路由嵌套"><a href="#路由嵌套" class="headerlink" title="路由嵌套"></a>路由嵌套</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;Route path=&quot;/films&quot; element=&#123;&lt;Film/&gt;&#125;&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​&lt;Route path=&quot;/film/nowplaying&quot; element=&#123;&#125;/&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​&lt;Route path=&quot;/film/comingsoon&quot; element=&#123;&#125;/&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;/Route&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&#x3D;&gt; 也可以略去 <code>path</code>中的 <code>/film/</code>直接使用 <code>“nowplaying”</code>直接表示相对film的路径</p><p><strong>路由容器</strong></p><p>&#x3D;&gt;给嵌套路由留位置</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;Outlet&gt;&lt;/Outlet&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="声明式导航和编程式导航"><a href="#声明式导航和编程式导航" class="headerlink" title="声明式导航和编程式导航"></a>声明式导航和编程式导航</h3><p><strong>声明式导航</strong></p><p>&#x3D;&gt;直接通过链接跳转</p><p><strong>react-rooter-dom</strong>中有个便签是 <code>NavLink</code> 可以直接做到切换组件页面，同时在点击链接是出现一个 <code>class=&quot;active&quot;</code>，但是 <code>active</code> 容易重名，故可以重新命名。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">className=&#123;(&#123;isActive&#125;)=&gt;isActive ? &quot;staractive&quot; : &quot;&quot;&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&#x2F;&#x2F;通过回调函数的形式进行命名，函数会自动传入一个 <code>&#123;isActive&#125;</code>参数</p><p><strong>编程式导航</strong></p><p>&#x3D;&gt;通过js编程进行跳转</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">const navigate = useNavigate()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">const handleFilmDetail = ()=&gt;&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​navigate(&quot;/detail&quot;)//在路径页面中加上detail路径</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;&gt; <strong>两种传参方式</strong></p><p>1.query（URL）传参&#x2F;detail?id&#x3D;1000…</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">navigate(`/detail=$&#123;id&#125;`)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>获取</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">const [searchParams,setSearchParams] = useSearchParams()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">console.log(searchParams.get(&quot;id&quot;))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">//searchParams.has(&#x27;id&#x27;)判断是否存在</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">//同时也可以通过setSearchParams方法改变路由，适用于猜你喜欢</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2.路由传参 &#x2F;detail&#x2F;1000</p><p>&#x3D;&gt;路由传参需要配置动态路径</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">navigate(`/detail/$&#123;id&#125;`)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;Route path=&#x27;/detail/:myid&#x27; element=&#123;&lt;Detail/&gt;&#125;&gt;&lt;/Route&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>获取</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">const params = useParams()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">console.log(params.myid)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="路由拦截"><a href="#路由拦截" class="headerlink" title="路由拦截"></a>路由拦截</h3><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;&gt;先进行判断是否能够跳转</p><p>&#x3D;&gt;类似未登陆时自动跳转到登录页面的作用</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;Route path=&#x27;/center&#x27; element=&#123;isAuth()?&lt;Center/&gt;:&lt;Redirect to=&#x27;/login&#x27;/&gt;&#125;&gt;&lt;/Route&gt;//三目只会执行一次，不会重新判断，需要改进</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;Route path=&#x27;/login&#x27; element=&#123;&lt;Login/&gt;&#125;&gt;&lt;/Route&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">function isAuth()&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​return localStorage.getItem(&quot;token&quot;)//判断是否登录</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;&gt;更新</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;Route path=&#x27;/center&#x27; element=&#123;&lt;Authcomponent&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;Center&gt;&lt;/Center&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;/Authcomponent&gt;&#125;&gt;&lt;/Route&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">function Authcomponent(&#123;children&#125;)&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​const isLogin = localStorage.getItem(&quot;token&quot;);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​return isLogin?childeren:&lt;Redirect to=&quot;/login&quot;/&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="路由模式"><a href="#路由模式" class="headerlink" title="路由模式"></a>路由模式</h3><p><strong>Hashrouter</strong></p><p>&#x3D;&gt;会是路径呈现前多出一个#，不会向后端请求路径</p><p><strong>BrowserRouter</strong></p><p>&#x3D;&gt;路径上没有#，会向<strong>后端</strong>请求接口</p><h3 id="withRouter"><a href="#withRouter" class="headerlink" title="withRouter"></a>withRouter</h3><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;&gt; <strong>类组件跳转页面方法</strong>，router6中不存在</p><p>使用类组件时需要自己封装一个 <code>withRouter</code>组件</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">erport default function withRouter(Component)&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​return function(props)&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​const push = useNavigate(); </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​const match = useParams();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​const location = useLocation();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​return &lt;Component &#123;...props&#125; history=&#123;&#123;push，match，location&#125;&#125;/&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>使用</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">export default withRouter(FilmItem_class)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>切换页面</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">handleClick(id)&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​this.props.history.push(`/detail/$&#123;id&#125;`)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;&gt;this.props.history.push()跳转页面</p><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;&gt;this.props.history.match()  获取参数</p><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;&gt;this.props.history.location()    获取当前路由</p><h3 id="useRouter"><a href="#useRouter" class="headerlink" title="useRouter"></a>useRouter</h3><p><strong>钩子配置路由</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">const element = useRoutes([&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​path:&#x27;&#x27;,//路径</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​element:LazyLoad.....//</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="路由懒加载"><a href="#路由懒加载" class="headerlink" title="路由懒加载"></a>路由懒加载</h3><p><strong>React.lazy 和 React.Suspense</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">const LazyLoad = (path) =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">const Comp = React.lazy(()=&gt;import(`../rooter/$&#123;path&#125;`))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​//回调函数导入路径</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​return (</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​&lt;React.Suspence fallback = &#123;&lt;&gt;加载中...&lt;/&gt;&#125;&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​//路由加载时显示的内容</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​&lt;Comp/&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​&lt;/React.Suspence&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;&gt; </p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;Route path=&#x27;/film&#x27; element=&#123;LazyLoad(&quot;film/Film&quot;)&#125;&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
